    "Flow (Csikszentmihalyi) as a related construct",
    "Tacit knowledge (Polanyi) as a related construct",
    "Technology acceptance (UTAUT / Davis) as a related construct",
    "Cognitive load (NASA-TLX, Sweller) as a related construct",
    "Experience sampling methodology",
    "High-performance sport coaching (tennis and padel)"
  ],
