  "publishingPrinciples": "All research outputs follow ISO 704 descriptive terminology conventions. Prior-art priority anchored via Zenodo DOI registration with Multi-Hash (SHA-256+SHA-512+SHA3-256+SHA3-512+BLAKE3) and standard timestamping on four independent calendars. Documentation layer (titles, descriptions, keywords) is treated as a living layer and may be refined post-publication for terminological consistency; substantive content (files) is fixed at publication time.",
